      "height": 260,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# State Token Schema\n\nThis is a deliberately small first proposal.\n\nThe goal is not to theme everything at once.\nThe goal is to create enough shared state language that ports, edges, labels, and node chrome stop improvising their own loudness.",
