    {
      "id": "state-token-schema-shape",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Token Shape",
      "position": {
        "x": 1420,
        "y": -180
      },
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "width": 420,
      "height": 340,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Token Shape\n\nStart with stateful properties, not raw colors:\n\n- `fg`\n- `bg`\n- `border`\n- `opacity`\n- `scale`\n- `shadow`\n- `labelOpacity`\n\nExample shape:\n```json\nstate.surface.calm.fg\nstate.surface.calm.border\nstate.surface.hover.shadow\nstate.surface.focused.scale\n```\n\nThe point is to encode meaning first, not paint values first.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-24T20:05:15Z",
            "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T01:20:00.000Z"
          },
          "intent": "graph",
          "meaning": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "defaults": {},
          "nodeDef": {
            "key": "markdown",
            "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
            "source": "local",
            "version": ">=0.1.0"
          },
          "views": [
            {
              "key": "markdown",
              "intent": "editor",
              "payload": "editor.web",
              "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
              "source": "local",
