    {
      "id": "state-token-schema-edge-map",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "How Edges / Labels Would Map",
      "position": {
        "x": 1900,
        "y": 260
      },
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 340,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# How Edges / Labels Would Map\n\n## Edges\n- `calm`: lower opacity, minimal shadow\n- `hover`: small emphasis bump, not a lightshow\n- `selected`: clearer stroke and contrast, restrained glow\n- `focused`: strongest ordinary line emphasis\n\n## Labels\n- default to quieter background and border\n- avoid black-on-white shoutiness\n- inherit selection/focus emphasis rather than using their own unrelated style language",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
